Suspension: It is a heterogeneous mixture in which solute particles do not dissolve but remains suspended throughout bulk of the medium and size of particles are more then 100 nanometer
For example:-
1) mixture of chalk and water
2) mixture of flour and water
3) muddy water
4) paints
5) mixture of magnesium hydroxide and water
properties of mixture
1) it is a hetero generous mixture
2) the particles of suspension can be seen through naked eyes
